<h3>🚀 Features</h3>
<ul>
    <li>🧩 DI-container awareness — <code>ContainerTrait</code>.</li>
    <li>💤 Lazy &amp; 🔒 lockable state — <code>LazyTrait</code>, <code>LockableTrait</code>.</li>
    <li>🆔 Identifiers — <code>IDTrait</code>, <code>QueryIDTrait</code>.</li>
    <li>🗂️ Config &amp; key-value access — <code>ConfigTrait</code>, <code>KeyValueTrait</code>, <code>JsonOptionsTrait</code>.</li>
    <li>🔗 URI building, stringable &amp; expression helpers — <code>UriTrait</code>, <code>ToStringTrait</code>, <code>strings\ExpressionTrait</code>.</li>
    <li>🧪 100% unit-test line coverage.</li>
</ul>

<h3>📦 Installation</h3>
<p>This library requires <a href="https://php.net/releases/" target="_blank">PHP 8.4+</a> and is installed via <a href="https://getcomposer.org/" target="_blank">Composer</a>:</p>
<pre class="language-bash prettyprint">composer require oihana/php-traits</pre>

